Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.80,0:05:04.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不 其實也…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.66,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不愧是繼任部長
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.66,0:05:08.89,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來來 我給你按按肩吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.89,0:05:10.47,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,喂… 笹原前輩!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.47,0:05:11.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:13.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\an8}沒事沒事～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.26,0:05:13.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笹原前輩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.44,0:05:15.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我本來就是因為對星星感興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:17.50,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並不是被加賀帶過來的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.89,0:05:19.21,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊勒 這樣嗎?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.21,0:05:20.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你們看起來關係很好的樣子還以為肯定在交往…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.86,0:05:21.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,並沒有!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.93,0:05:24.23,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我和七瀨只是單純的家很近而已
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.30,0:05:26.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一說是青梅竹馬就總這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:28.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我對七瀨可是什麼想法都沒有!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.84,0:05:30.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也什麼想法都沒有!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:34.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且加賀他 似乎有其他喜歡的人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.08,0:05:36.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,唔欸! 是這樣嗎加賀君?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.02,0:05:37.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,才沒呢 這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真的嘛～ 雖說看你這樣就大概知道了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.28,0:05:43.39,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要我幫你猜猜嗎～? 嗯～～～?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.89,0:05:48.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笹原 坂本老師說找你有事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.58,0:05:51.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦～ 正是關鍵時刻的說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.31,0:05:54.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我等下再來聽後續啊～
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然是笹原前輩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.20,0:06:04.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想想加賀你也不會對星星有興趣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.60,0:06:05.85,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,看上前輩了對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.96,0:06:07.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以說不是了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.48,0:06:09.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,而且這和七瀨你沒關係吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.29,0:06:10.92,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼總是關心這種事情啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,想你快點被拒絕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.16,0:06:17.45,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼啊! 我得罪你啦!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.51,0:06:20.55,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你從上中學後開始 就一直無視我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.02,0:06:22.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就因為怕被周圍同學嘲笑
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.11,0:06:24.61,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還不是七瀨你說不要的吧!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.68,0:06:26.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說要是被誤解為那種關係的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.51,0:06:28.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是不想被認為和你關係很好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.16,0:06:30.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤!? 這我也不想啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊～這樣啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.12,0:06:33.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,超不想和我有什麼緋聞的是吧!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.94,0:06:37.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼鬼啊!? 我這邊不是在為七瀨你擔心嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.85,0:06:39.54,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,說什麼為我擔心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.60,0:06:41.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明就是你突然不理我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.52,0:06:44.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,七瀨你不也是 突然就開始討厭我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是加賀你先討厭我的!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:49.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,哪邊先都無所謂吧 反正是相互討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.88,0:06:52.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,要是討厭你的話哪會和你上一個學校啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.93,0:06:54.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤…蛤!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.61,0:06:56.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,完全不懂你在說什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.87,0:06:58.87,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,笨蛋加賀! 還不懂我嗎!?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.65,0:07:01.72,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,明明和其他女孩子可以很正常的說話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.31,0:07:03.71,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就單單無視我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.86,0:07:05.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不… 我沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.37,0:07:08.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,就算如此你對別人看起來也沒太關心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.91,0:07:11.57,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我還一直以為你對別的女生應該沒什麼興趣的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.08,0:07:13.81,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,等等… 你冷靜一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.25,0:07:16.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼 是笹原前輩啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.98,0:07:18.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.76,0:07:22.34,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,知道了啦對不起是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:25.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒有考慮到七瀨的心情
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.03,0:07:28.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一直 在為我的事情擔心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.27,0:07:31.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那個 因為
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.19,0:07:34.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我是你青梅竹馬
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.22,0:07:38.73,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你是我青梅竹馬怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.83,0:07:40.24,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,你什麼都沒搞明白不是!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.40,0:07:41.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,咦 你不是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.46,0:07:44.09,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真以為我為加賀你做這麼多…  就只是…!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.37,0:07:45.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.39,0:07:46.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是說不討厭我嗎…剛才
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.95,0:07:48.22,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,最討厭你啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.34,0:07:51.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,到 到底還是討厭我啊!!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.72,0:07:53.44,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那你跑到天文部來到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.70,0:07:54.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,來氣我的…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.99,0:08:00.29,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,久等啦～
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.29,0:08:02.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那～加賀君你喜歡的女孩子到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.81,0:08:08.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.25,0:08:09.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,{\pos(174.4,586.8)\fs40\c&H001E1E1E\b1\bord0}結\N束
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.41,0:08:13.49,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟喜歡的人告白 然後在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.12,0:08:16.38,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但那之後總感覺…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.93,0:08:19.40,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,變得有些拘謹
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.47,0:08:22.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛 剛田君
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.81,0:08:23.93,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,今天一起回…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.93,0:08:24.74,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉上根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.00,0:08:26.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我還有社團活動 下次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.37,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是不是做朋友比較好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.01,0:08:33.43,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不不不 這才剛開始交往呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.69,0:08:35.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我應該更加主動一點才…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.84,0:08:37.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,怎麼了上根
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.86,0:08:39.17,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,還沒回家嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:44.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.99,0:08:46.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我也有一些事情沒做完留下來了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.00,0:08:49.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 讓你等我才是不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.10,0:08:51.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我社團活動的時候也會待到比較晚
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.89,0:08:52.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以以後一起…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.68,0:08:54.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 太晚了很危險的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.14,0:08:56.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒 沒關係的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.63,0:08:58.18,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是有剛田君在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:09:00.16,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 我只能送你到公車站
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.31,0:09:04.79,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,果然他其實不願和我交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.21,0:09:07.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,給他增添麻煩了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.78,0:09:10.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不會的 剛田君只是太溫柔了而已
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.17,0:09:12.65,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,一直以來都是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.33,0:09:18.96,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,剛剛… 是躲開我了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:20.60,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,躲開我了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.40,0:09:24.15,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,社團活動出了汗所以在意嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.53,0:09:25.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.72,0:09:26.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是這樣的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.06,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,其實並不是在躲著我…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.73,0:09:32.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,上根 可以不要這樣了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.66,0:09:38.95,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我應該早點跟你說的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.01,0:09:41.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟人交往我也是第一次
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.22,0:09:43.70,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也在學習該如何做
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.34,0:09:45.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是我也考慮過了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.54,0:09:47.42,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這樣下去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:48.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.29,0:09:51.28,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以希望上根能放輕鬆一些
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:53.08,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.94,0:09:54.75,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.00,0:09:56.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,本不該這樣子說的但…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.00,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 謝謝你跟我說
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.54,0:10:02.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,謝謝你跟我交往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.54,0:10:05.99,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,對不起 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.24,0:10:08.91,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱 抱歉 我沒打算把你弄哭來著
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.34,0:10:13.07,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,沒事 我們還能回到以前那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.14,0:10:15.83,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是呢 但和以前完全一樣也不現實…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.41,0:10:19.80,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也是啊 都是我的錯 變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.46,0:10:22.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下次要不要試著牽牽手?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:24.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,畢竟是戀人嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.87,0:10:30.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,什麼意思?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.57,0:10:32.41,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我太急了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.68,0:10:35.56,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是 剛剛像要分手一樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.68,0:10:36.51,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,分手!?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.85,0:10:38.25,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我可沒說這種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.85,0:10:41.03,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,只是想互相之間注意些 別那麼拘謹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.16,0:10:43.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,能再稍微輕鬆一點什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.63,0:10:46.05,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,難道說 只有我很在意這問題嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.27,0:10:47.68,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 是我誤會了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.88,0:10:52.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 那什麼 剛在一起就擺出一副男朋友的架子也很奇怪吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.43,0:10:57.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以那個 本想儘可能像平時那樣相處…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.42,0:10:58.88,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,但是這樣又不會太冷淡了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.36,0:11:02.12,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,所以想先關心一下你回家的安全什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.23,0:11:03.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,是我多管閒事了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.49,0:11:10.46,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那…剛剛我靠近你的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.65,0:11:12.02,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,為什麼避開了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.71,0:11:15.84,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,這個…因為社團活動出了汗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.69,0:11:18.76,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不 其實是因為有點害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.81,0:11:37.36,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,我真是個笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.56,0:11:38.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是傻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.64,0:11:44.78,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 我什麼都沒看到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.95,0:11:46.86,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不是這樣的 剛剛是七瀨她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.45,0:11:51.58,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.94,0:11:53.04,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.06,0:11:56.98,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,優樹 去給七瀨家送點蘋果吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.63,0:11:59.67,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,不要 媽媽你自己去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.23,0:12:01.48,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,幹嘛這麼不願意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.56,0:12:02.90,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,跟小薰吵架了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.28,0:12:06.26,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,也不是這樣 總覺得自己被討厭著
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.60,0:12:09.53,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,蛤? 小薰喜歡你的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.38,0:12:13.19,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,啊 這還是秘密嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.30,0:12:14.77,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,抱歉 不算不算 忘了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.88,0:12:24.32,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,那 那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.83,0:12:29.52,Tsurezure Children,,0,0,0,,下集 我們不需要女孩
